<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activation de compte</title>
    <style>
        .elipse1{
            background: radial-gradient(81.25% 81.25% at 67.32% 18.75%, #5740EE 0%, #9740EE 100%) ;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 100px 10px rgba(34, 215, 226, 0.3);
            transform: rotate(30deg);
            position: fixed;
            width: 190px;
            height: 190px;
            left: 10%;
            top: -40px;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .elipse2{
            background: radial-gradient(81.25% 81.25% at 67.32% 18.75%, #5740EE 0%,#9740EE 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 100px 10px rgba(34, 215, 226, 0.3);
            transform: rotate(30deg);
            position: fixed;
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            right: 15%;
            top: 10%;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .elipse3{
            background: radial-gradient(81.25% 81.25% at 67.32% 18.75%,  #5740EE 0%, #9740EE 100%) ;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 100px 10px rgba(34, 215, 226, 0.3);
            transform: rotate(30deg);
            position: fixed;
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            right: 30%;
            bottom: 5%;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .fond-gris{

             display: flex;

            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            height:350px;
            right: 5%;
            top: 25%;
            text-align: center;

        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #1E1D2B;
        }

        table {
            width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }



        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: #2B2C3E;
            border-radius: 24px;
            color: white;


        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            table{
                width: 100% !important;
            }
        }


        .button {

            border-radius: 24px;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: radial-gradient(81.25% 81.25% at 67.32% 18.75%,  #5740EE 0%, #9740EE 100%) ;
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container{
            margin-left: 0% !important;
            margin-right: 0%!important;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        table{
            width: 40%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="elipse1"></div>
    <div class="elipse2"></div>
    <div class="elipse3"></div>
    <div class="fond-gris">

        <table>
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <h1>Réinitialisation du mot de passe</h1>
                    <h3>Salut {{ user.pseudo }} </h3>
                    <p> Voici le lien pour réinitialiser ton mot de passe,<br>
                        clique sur le bouton ci-dessous :</p>
                    <div class="button-container">
                        <a href="{{server}}/activation/{{ user.token }}" target="_blank" class="button">Réinitialisé mon mot de passe</a>
                    </div>
                    <p>Si le bouton ne fonctionne pas,<br> copie-colle le lien suivant dans ton navigateur :</p>
                    <p>{{server}}/resetpassword/{{user.token}}</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

